{
  "registry": "aaif-memory-backends",
  "sc_standard": "SC-006",
  "description": "Storage backends for memory[].backend (SPECIFICATION §H). A runtime that does not have the named backend SHOULD substitute a compatible one (e.g. another vector store) unless the agent pins it via required_capabilities[].",
